value.0: Good God <man/woman>!  I don't have time to talk right now!
Do I know you?
Weapons... I need lots of weapons...
I... I just can't take it...
They've barred the gates!  There's no way out!
They're everywhere!  Everywhere!
Madness!
We must fight them!  Fight back!
The end in nigh!
Everyone I know died... the problem is... they didn't stay dead...
Where did they all come from?!?
Get away from me <bitch/bastard>!  I'm getting out of here!
Where are the militia?!?   Where is the town guard?!?
Fly you fools!
We've got to get out of here!
Help me... Save my family...
I... I don't feel so well...
We're doomed!  We're all gonna die!
Please... what's happening here?!?
Run!  Run for your lives!
Hello there, need another sword arm?
You understand I'm putting my life on the line.  50 gold now and I'll serve you for a year.
<StartCheck>[Botch]</Start>  How dare you insult me in this way!  Are you saying my feeble life isn't WORTH it to you?
<StartCheck>[Failure]</Start>  You are a persuasive <man/woman>, but the money I ask for is to support my family.  I cannot take any less.
<StartCheck>[Success]</Start>  It seems I cannot resist a leader such as yourself.  I will accept 25 gold for a year.
Then I accept your command
Yes... what do you require of me?
I am too weak from last time <Master/Mistress>
Of course, <Master/Mistress>
As you wish.
<StartAction>*Removes several potions and salves from <his/her> pack and carefully checks for cuts and bruises, tending each in turn.</Start>
What would you like to change?
So be it then, I'll be here if you need me.
Verywell, I shall used my melee weapons.
Verywell, I shall used my ranged weapons.
I'm sorry, I cannot do business with the likes of you.
<StartCheck>[Failure]</Start>  I told you my answer was no!
<StartCheck>[Success]</Start>  I'm sorry.  You are persuasive, but not persuasive enough.
<StartCheck>[Success]</Start>  Very well.  You are a hard one to resist.  Would you consider hiring me to stand at your defense?
You understand I'm putting my life on the line.  50 gold now and I'll serve you for a year.
<StartCheck>[Botch]</Start>  How dare you insult me in this way!  Are you saying my feeble life isn't WORTH it to you?
<StartCheck>[Failure]</Start>  You are a persuasive <man/woman>, but the money I ask for is to support my family.  I cannot take any less.
<StartCheck>[Success]</Start>  It seems I cannot resist a leader such as yourself.  I will accept 25 gold for a year.
Then I accept your command
Do not speak to me again!
I'm not going any further that way...
Nevermind.
It depends, what do you charge for it?
I don't have that sort of money on me at this time.  I will return later.
My good man, we offer adventure and excitement, not war.  How about 25 gold for a year?  <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start>
I don't have that sort of money on me at this time.  I will return later.
I do not have 25 gold on me now, but I will return later.
Done
Deal
Right, follow me
Good to have you on board.
Hold still, I need to feed...
Good servant...
I need you to tend to your wounds.
Nothing more.
I belive its time we parted ways.
If I fail to open a lock, do not aid me.
If I fail to open a lock, aid me.
I need you to be more stealthy
I'd like you to stop traveling so quietly.
I'd like you to search all the time.
Do not search all the time anymore.
I'd like to change how you heal me.
I'd like to change how close you are to me.
Do not use ranged weapons anymore, only melee.
Do not use melee weapons anymore, only ranged.
